source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04101_000010_ALGUS<tab>Who dares disturb the slumber of Argath Thadalfus, rightful king of Ivalice!?
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04101_000010_ALGUS<tab>“Je suis Argath, roi d'Ivalice<var 1D /var>! Qui ose troubler mon sommeil<var 1D /var>?”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04101_000011_ALGUS<tab>Descendants of House Beoulve? Then by my sword shall I banish your souls to the deepest hell!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04101_000011_ALGUS<tab>“Des descendants de la maison Beoulve<var 1D /var>? Dans ce cas, de mon épée, je vais détruire vos âmes<var 1D /var>!”

source: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04101_000020_ALGUS<tab>Where... Where am I? This body... It is not my own. Oh, gods, what have I done? Save me Ramza! Save me!
target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_04101_000020_ALGUS<tab>“Mais que fais-je... ici<var 1D /var>!?<var 1D /var>... Et qu'est-il... arrivé à mon corps<var 1D /var>!?<var 1D /var>... Au secours... Ramza<var 1D /var>!<var 1D /var>...”
